data.description: The opportunity you have been waiting for has arrived. Just under 40 acres in Calhan Zoned A-35 for Agricultural. The perfect place for your horses, and/or pretty much anything you could want to use this incredible span of land for. With 3 beds and 2 baths and a 2 car detached garage. There is also another mobile home on the property that could be fixed up and made a great additional livable space. Bring your offers today as it likely won't be available for long.
